x Priest named Saint Nicholaos who lived in the 4th century AD. His monastery, where he lived and was later buried, is located in Demre, Antalya in today's Turkey.<br>\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><u><em>(Do not refresh your page, proceed option will be visible in 30 seconds.)</em></u></span>","DataExportTag":"control","QuestionID":"QID1715521524"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3k23UO2PJvuYb66","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1715521525","SecondaryAttribute":"Timing","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Timing","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"Timing","Selector":"PageTimer","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","MaxSeconds":"0"},"QuestionDescription":"Timing","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"First Click"},"2":{"Display":"Last Click"},"3":{"Display":"Page Submit"},"4":{"Display":"Click Count"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":188,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Timing","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"DataExportTag":"time_control","QuestionID":"QID1715521525"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3k23UO2PJvuYb66","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1715521526","SecondaryAttribute":"A news article that recently received national attention demonstrates how few elites, governments...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"A news article that recently received national attention demonstrates how few elites, governments, political parties, and technology companies collaborate to secretly monitor our lives and manipulate our behavior. The article shows that these technology companies are using our location history, search history, purchase history, and audio files. and sell our data to governments and political parties.<br>\n<br>\nThe article further illustrates that these companies provide our personalized data to almost all politicians on either side of the aisle to manipulate us and sway our vote choice for their own benefit. It sadly concluded that no political party, administration, or leader has acted against such extensive violations of privacy because of the clear benefit to all governments, political parties, and politicians.<br>\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><u><em>(Do not refresh your page, proceed option will be visible in 30 seconds.)</em></u></span>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"A news article that recently received national attention demonstrates how few elites, governments...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":19,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"A news article that recently received national attention demonstrates how governments, political parties, and technology companies collaborate to secretly monitor our lives and manipulate our behavior. The article shows that these technology companies are using our location history, search history, purchase history, and audio files. and sell our data to governments and political parties.<br>\n<br>\nThe article further illustrates that these companies provide our personalized data to almost all politicians on either side of the aisle to manipulate us and sway our vote choice for their own benefit. It sadly concluded that no political party, administration, or leader has acted against such extensive violations of privacy because of the clear benefit to all governments, political parties, and politicians.<br>\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><u><em>(Do not refresh your page, proceed option will be visible in 30 seconds.)</em></u></span>","DataExportTag":"vignette_nonpartisan","QuestionID":"QID1715521526"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3k23UO2PJvuYb66","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1715521527","SecondaryAttribute":"Timing","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Timing","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"Timing","Selector":"PageTimer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"H