an Party and technology companies are currently collaborating to manipulate the 2024 election by influencing our vote choice. The article shows that these technology companies are using our location history, search history, purchase history, and audio files.<br>\n<br>\nThe article goes on to present newly leaked documents from the GOP's plans to use our data to sway the 2024 Presidential elections for the Republicans. It also summarizes a recent announcement made by Democrats;&nbsp; they are going to “stand up for America and defend our elections.”<br>\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><u><em>(Do not refresh your page, proceed option will be visible in 30 seconds.)</em></u></span>","DataExportTag":"vignette_democratic","QuestionID":"QID1715521528"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3k23UO2PJvuYb66","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1715521529","SecondaryAttribute":"Timing","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Timing","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"Timing","Selector":"PageTimer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","MaxSeconds":"0","MinSeconds":15},"QuestionDescription":"Timing","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"First Click"},"2":{"Display":"Last Click"},"3":{"Display":"Page Submit"},"4":{"Display":"Click Count"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":288,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Timing","DataExportTag":"time_democratic","QuestionID":"QID1715521529"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3k23UO2PJvuYb66","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1715521530","SecondaryAttribute":"A news article that received national attention recently reveals how few secret groups determined an","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"A news article that recently received national attention demonstrates how few elites, the Democratic Party and technology companies are currently collaborating to manipulate the 2024 election by influencing our vote choice. The article shows that these technology companies make revenue by selling our location history, search history, purchase history, and audio files.<br>\n<br>\nThe article goes on to present newly leaked documents from the Biden administration’s plans to use our data to sway the 2024 Presidential elections for Democrats. It also summarizes a recent announcement made by the Republicans; they are going to “stand up for America and defend our elections.”<br>\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><u><em>(Do not refresh your page, proceed option will be visible in 30 seconds.)</em></u></span>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"SpecifyLabel"},"QuestionDescription":"A news article that received national attention recently reveals how few secret groups determined an","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":74,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"A news article that recently received national attention demonstrates how the Democratic Party and technology companies are currently collaborating to manipulate the 2024 election by influencing our vote choice. The article shows that these technology companies make revenue by selling our location history, search history, purchase history, and audio files.<br>\n<br>\nThe article goes on to present newly leaked documents from the Biden administration’s plans to use our data to sway the 2024 Presidential elections for Democrats. It also summarizes a recent announcement made by the Republicans; they are going to “stand up for America and defend our elections.”<br>\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;\"><u><em>(Do not refresh your page, proceed option will be visible in 30 seconds.)</em></u></span>","DataExportTag":"vignette_republican","QuestionID":"QID1715521530"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3k23UO2PJvuYb66","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1715521531","SecondaryAttribute":"Timing","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{