e power of Presidents in American politics. Some people argue that Pres...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"People talk a lot about the power of Presidents in American politics. Some people argue that Presidents should have more power and some do not. Now, we will present you some statements that proposes new powers for the Presidents to possess.<br>Please indicate how much you agree or disagree&nbsp;to the following statements.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"normerosion","QuestionID":"QID188","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"RepeatHeaders":"none","WhiteSpace":"OFF","MobileFirst":true,"ChoiceColumnWidthPixels":391},"QuestionDescription":"People talk a lot about the power of Presidents in American politics. Some people argue that Pres...","Choices":{"2":{"Display":"The President may change electoral laws even if it is against the interests of the opposition parties."},"3":{"Display":"The President may disqualify candidates of other parties from running for office."},"8":{"Display":"The President may please select prefer not to answer if you are reading this statement."},"10":{"Display":"The President may open lawsuits and prosecute citizens who criticize them or their administration."},"12":{"Display":"The President may close political parties."},"13":{"Display":"The President may run for a third and a fourth term even though the constitution limits their term to two."}},"ChoiceOrder":["2","3","8","10","12","13"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":19,"NextAnswerId":12,"Answers":{"4":{"Display":"Strongly disagree"},"11":{"Display":"Disagree"},"5":{"Display":"Somewhat disagree"},"7":{"Display":"Somewhat agree"},"10":{"Display":"Agree"},"8":{"Display":"Strongly agree"},"9":{"Display":"Prefer not to answ