e back our country by exposing their backroom deals and putting power back in the hands of ordinary people where it belongs.&quot;</em>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"struc_pop","QuestionID":"QID382","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please read this brief statement from a politician’s speech. This statement was made during their...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3k23UO2PJvuYb66","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID383","SecondaryAttribute":"\"When a small number of wealthy or well-connected people have too much influence over government,...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"\"When a small number of wealthy or well-connected people have too much influence over government, it stops working for ordinary citizens and serves narrow interests instead.\"","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"populism","QuestionID":"QID383","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"\"When a small number of wealthy or well-connected people have too much influence over government,...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3k23UO2PJvuYb66","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID384","SecondaryAttribute":"\"A small group of wealthy and well-connected people secretly pull the strings of government, so i...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"\"A small group of wealthy and well-connected people secretly pull the strings of government, so it no longer truly represents ordinary citizens.\"","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"conspiracism","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVis